Docker -: The Next Generation platform service
Info about Docker

The most amazing software based platform service ever
used by most companies
docker is free for everyone

Developement info
Solomon Hykes is the core developer
Docker Inc is the company
written in Go lang
Public release
docker released in December 21, 2013

Platform supported
Linux kernel 3.10 and later
Mac Os
Windows server 2016 and later
study and software details
For offical website you can browse docker docs
For docker images you can browser docker hub

Bash Completion for Docker
you can download it from

sudo curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/docker/docker-ce/master/components/cli/contrib/completion/bash/docker -o /etc/bash_completion.d/docker.sh
